de.hshl.obj.wavefront.Wavefront.ObjectLoader

  • Packages that use Wavefront.ObjectLoader 
    Package Description
    de.hshl.obj.wavefront
    This package contains all classes required to load wavefront data, forming the core of the library.

      Wavefront.ObjectLoader Wavefront.ObjectLoader.ignoreMaterials()
      Do not load any materials from the file.

      Do not load any surface normals from the file.
      Wavefront.ObjectLoader Wavefront.ObjectLoader.ignoreStructures()
      Ignore any OBJ structures like groups or objects and load everything into a single object instead.
